// Effective (turbulent) diffusivity of the passive pollutant.
// Crude constant stand-in for nut/Sct (Sct ~ 0.7); 1-2 m^2/s is typical.
// A spatially-varying DT from the frozen nut is a later refinement.
DT              DT [0 2 -1 0 0 0 0] 1.0;


